data.description: Step into your dream oasis with this stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home, built in 2012. Featuring an open floor plan, two living areas, this home offers a seamless blend of modern elegance and comfort. Outside, a complete backyard paradise awaits, featuring a gazebo and a soothing water fountain. Inside, you'll find a convenient home office, extra-high cabinets in the kitchen, an oversized pantry for all your storage needs, and a wrap-around bar perfect for casual dining or entertaining. The oversized garage provides ample space for your vehicles and additional storage. This home is the perfect retreat for both relaxation and entertaining.
